# Grasp
Graph with ASP made easy.


## CLI example


    grasp split data.lp -o "data_{}.lp" # split a graph by cc
    grasp split data.lp


## CLI commands

- `split`: split by connected component
- `info`: give info about given graph
- `clean`: rewrite the graph in a clean ASP version
